request.description:
New conversation, non-streaming. Auto-saves `conversation_id` to collection variable.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "id": "chatcmpl-...",
  "object": "chat.completion",
  "model": "gemini",
  "conversation_id": "conv_...",
  "choices": [{
    "index": 0,
    "message": { "role": "assistant", "content": "..." },
    "finish_reason": "stop"
  }],
  "usage": { "prompt_tokens": 0, "completion_tokens": 0, "total_tokens": 0 }
}
```

