request.description:
Real SSE streaming. Tokens appear progressively as Gemini generates them.

**SSE Format:**
```
data: {"id":"chatcmpl-...","object":"chat.completion.chunk","choices":[{"delta":{"role":"assistant","content":"..."},"finish_reason":null}]}

data: {"id":"chatcmpl-...","choices":[{"delta":{"content":"..."},"finish_reason":null}]}

data: {"id":"chatcmpl-...","choices":[{"delta":{},"finish_reason":"stop"}]}

data: [DONE]
```

Each chunk contains `conversation_id` for continuation.
